Package: reach.viz
Title: Flood Visualisation Module for the Flode Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jonathan", "Payne", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jonathan.payne@environment-agency.gov.uk")
Description: Standardised ggplot2-compatible chart themes and flood-specific
    plot functions for the F&W team's Flode R package ecosystem. Provides a
    consistent visual identity (theme_flood, QC flag scales, condition rating
    scales) and a catalogue of plot functions covering hydrometric time series,
    ensemble forecasts, model performance validation, condition assessment, and
    model cascade diagrams. All data manipulation uses data.table; no tidyverse
    dependency.
